OL,5, Boris Johnson "wanted to be injected   
OL,6, with Covid-19 on television" to calm   
OL,7, public fears, an ex-aide has said.     
OL,9,FThe claim - by Lord Lister - came in a 
OL,10,Fwitness statement to the Covid inquiry.
OL,12,FHe said Mr Johnson "suggested to senior
OL,13,Fcivil servants and advisers that he    
OL,14,Fwanted to be injected with Covid-19 on 
OL,15,Ftelevision to demonstrate to the public
OL,16,Fthat it did not pose a threat."        
OL,18,FIt was "at a time when Covid was not   
OL,19,Fseen as being the serious disease it   
OL,20,Fsubsequently became," he added.        
